Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有很多甜食喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不全是苦的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯那種錯的話可真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯那產的哈齊瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊 媽媽 我可是做得最棒的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特 王都你是第一次來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 小時候來過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被老爸帶著來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.82,0:01:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 我聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 我們回毗儺天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三台在後方負責警戒和偵查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被人發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.07,0:02:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方有難民過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行引導工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避難船回來之前待命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護軍隊生活用品的運送
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中部避難所發生事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民間的代表不是應該已經定下來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碼頭的收容準備工作怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍茲爾陛下在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓運輸車過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公園廣場集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍茲爾陛下也不知哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向東環狀外門移動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 衛兵到底在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:48.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}特別なものは何もないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:04:01.93,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}その手に掴むには　充分すぎる愛を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:16.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}信じるものを持っている者は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:31.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}揺るぎない愛の為に貫く想いを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:39.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}運命に立ち向かえるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:49.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}この全て懸ける想いでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:48.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}雖無甚特別之物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:04:01.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}卻有愛滿溢雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:16.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}心有所信之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:31.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}傾注思念 只為不渝大愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:39.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}若注定直面命運
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:49.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}唯有付出一切 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:11.41,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000}慟哭之城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得你會遲到啊 伊奧上校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼克戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍 這種大風天氣下增援部隊都遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 完全不影響我們的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他們到的時候戰鬥已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們在被佔領的毗儺天歡迎他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦爾基裡斯部隊的一位名叫克萊歐的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說一直被扣押在毗儺天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是薩布拉夫家的千金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:05:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然消息不一定可靠…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我前去確認下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有此事的話便把她救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我們要進攻王宮 攻陷毗儺天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能救出這位小姐 確實能在國內成為一段佳話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這與我毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來向毗儺天進發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在毗儺天的王宮見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜爾維他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個找到的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的大部隊開始行動了 有90台機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯準備趁著天黑一口氣攻過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不能在這過多停留了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 全員登機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金 洛金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金 洛金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜爾維 怎麼了 軍服破破爛爛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈爾哥 不會是幽靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我自己都覺得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過確實還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿特內斯大部隊應該正前往毗儺天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得想辦法先到一步進行補給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法？ 難道要用這法布尼爾跑一晚上？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半路遇到敵人怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正好 就當武器的補給了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁他們不注意偷襲他們就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也想不到有人會用這台法布尼爾進攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向西瓊大人報告 物資已經運達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓難民上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比空手回去強多了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運來的石英比克里修那的硬度更高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請注意一下 打磨機可能會折斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不能花太長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告說他已經和巴爾德將軍匯合 向這邊趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜爾維他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的市民中20%可以收容在王城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從北方避難者的人數來看…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在確保登船工作順利進行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水和糧食的儲備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概能維持2個月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有了這些就能爭取到和歐蘭德的交涉時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 那個波爾庫斯將軍正在向這大舉進攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕明早就到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守備的格雷姆有60台 要是被那個人突破防線的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛大隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況我已經清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究沒法…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗命運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們搶在波爾庫斯前到達王都的幾率很小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做好沒有補給就開始戰鬥的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特 再次啟動帝爾鋒之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有遭遇敵人的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我藏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方把我放下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 沒想到能得到這麼大塊的石英
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對這打磨機來說負擔太好像重了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我並不是反對王妃大人的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能用作最後工序
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用於最初打孔的話 我有更好的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來還能節省時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在才開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的船上準備了各種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應有盡有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 估計有90台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯 竟公然從正面攻來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾德將軍沒能趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始一級防禦戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲 開始一級防禦戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一號 第一種配備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東外門以及東門配備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓他們進入王都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機嗎 已經追上來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯 王都好像想讓我們吃個閉門羹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲敲門讓他們放我們進去訪問下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各隊 散開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位 化身野獸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西面27台 東面18台 部隊已經散開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要從正面攻來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 請去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 市民都避難了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難民呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達這裡的就是全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已經沒法接近毗儺天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了從陸路迂迴到庫恩魯已經派出了救援隊 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以替換了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韌帶準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕佳的防禦位置麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴蒂斯將軍已經和艾爾特密斯·改部隊匯合了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是專攻遠程射擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹的漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此寒酸的歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺勇猛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入第二防禦態勢 把他們封鎖在北門內
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這 和西瓊大人推斷的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接韌帶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強化連接的準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓那一大捆韌帶動起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是讓韌帶動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要的是能承受那份重量的強度和韌度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接用的韌帶怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下 我馬上去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊大人 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準很精確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你們向前一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會就想憑這麼點人來阻止我們的突破吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 要被東門那邊佔了先機麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去確保北門到這裡的移動通路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來把他們全部擊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的改良機種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴爾德將軍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會從背後過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分別對付各自目標 祝各位成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個和這個 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責看守的兩位也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在製造能打敗你們國家格雷姆的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有帝爾鋒能用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等萊卡特回來就交給他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.27,0:21:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒有收到他回來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平安回來的話 我就不生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊歐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也想和你做個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要出發了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們過去 開火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是巴爾德將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.27,0:23:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能把我們擋在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是時間緊迫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我們先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那些村民 你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.39,0:24:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里修那這個國家已經注定要滅亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.86,0:24:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這幫蠻族
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.66,0:24:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是覺得現在是在打仗所以沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.56,0:24:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人的死給你的擔子太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.87,0:24:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲哀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.13,0:24:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道結果如何 也不得不竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.86,0:25:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也利用建築物陰影的掩蔽繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.61,0:25:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迅速前往會合地點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.07,0:25:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧上校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.35,0:25:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊特 繼續後方掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.72,0:25:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.01,0:25:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.47,0:25:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來掩護上校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.74,0:25:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然比預定提前到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.08,0:25:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.73,0:25:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了 萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.61,0:25:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.81,0:25:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像還不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.44,0:26:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你無法守護身後王宮的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.18,0:26:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就已經有辱使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.47,0:26:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.82,0:26:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊 萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.41,0:26:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑銀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.46,0:26:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看你用過彈射槍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.97,0:27:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.67,0:27:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是未知格雷姆的特性麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.13,0:27:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是只是駕駛員的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.59,0:27:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.29,0:27:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把王宮打下來 然後再慢慢確認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請調整到完全張緊的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.17,0:27:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊大人 請您退後
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.99,0:27:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再緊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.93,0:27:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是來真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.90,0:27:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊大人 帝爾鋒已經返回了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.21,0:27:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.05,0:27:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧找到它時是在啟動待機中 已經安裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.46,0:27:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在交戰中 沿中央大道朝這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.24,0:27:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.12,0:27:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.21,0:27:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北門…被法布尼爾的殘骸…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.91,0:27:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.01,0:28:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和赤手空拳的敵人打 那只是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.37,0:28:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.59,0:28:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是跳得這麼高啊 黑銀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.73,0:28:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.33,0:28:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在古代戰爭書籍中讀到過
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.51,0:28:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書上說兩國戰到終局時會互相投石
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.52,0:28:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 可沒想到居然在這裡也能見到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.86,0:28:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這樣下去胳膊就…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.61,0:29:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個似乎也曾讀到過 互毆好像也是兵法的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.97,0:29:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這防禦不錯 不過靠這個可沒法保衛國家
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.58,0:29:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它們連接在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.90,0:29:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保持韌帶的強度 請盡可能繫緊一些
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.27,0:29:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎有些地方弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.32,0:29:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 黑銀的力量與我們不可同日而語
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.67,0:29:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這力量並不是來自駕駛員的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:30:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎駕駛員也是和我們完全不同的異類
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.07,0:30:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是從古代甦醒而來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.92,0:30:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 他還有什麼別的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.31,0:30:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三內門被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.52,0:30:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西側防線交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.37,0:30:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從東面進來的部隊正向中央移動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.72,0:30:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須回去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.12,0:30:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.74,0:30:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去包抄他們 在立交橋處將敵人擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.54,0:30:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.30,0:30:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.07,0:30:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.93,0:30:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王宮在閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.99,0:30:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 決不讓敵人靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.82,0:31:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.63,0:31:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的戰術本身就讓人難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.78,0:31:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.91,0:32:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 就沒考慮過重量的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.52,0:32:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.41,0:32:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要的不是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.50,0:32:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼不用彈射槍呢 石英傳導沒出故障啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.38,0:32:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見多了那些自稱精英的無能者
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.54,0:32:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是像這種據說以百萬分之一的概率降生的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.88,0:32:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還從沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.86,0:32:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然 真的存在麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.90,0:32:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特呢 帝爾鋒在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.46,0:32:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在立交橋附近戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.22,0:32:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.27,0:32:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.33,0:32:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為武器看起來很原始是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.56,0:33:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是原始嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.11,0:33:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 駕駛員萊卡特·阿羅 他不能使用魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.60,0:33:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.64,0:33:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.39,0:33:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝爾鋒是古代技術所製造的 操縱極其困難
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.42,0:33:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知為何 身為無能者飽受歧視的萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.19,0:33:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他才能開動帝爾鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.17,0:33:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在原因還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.41,0:33:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個駕駛員就可以使用這武器是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.67,0:33:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔力以外的某種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.66,0:33:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.26,0:33:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他是個怪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.56,0:33:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備就緒 帝爾鋒那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.96,0:33:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把大門打開 帝爾鋒那邊我去說明
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.98,0:33:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.11,0:33:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.62,0:33:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向第一內門移動
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.86,0:33:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把那東西運到門那去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.39,0:34:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無魔力者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.07,0:34:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傑斯隊的克萊歐·薩布拉夫閣下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是波爾庫斯大隊所屬的伊奧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.47,0:34:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的 我是傑斯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.93,0:34:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦爾基裡斯隊的克萊歐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.06,0:34:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.17,0:34:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.00,0:34:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定把您送回阿特內斯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.40,0:34:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.65,0:34:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.10,0:34:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 西瓊姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.04,0:35:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次那傢伙  看我收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.11,0:35:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密密麻麻地都鑽進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.43,0:35:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 這韌帶事到如今己經毫無用處了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.14,0:35:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.74,0:35:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.40,0:35:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.00,0:35:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 萊卡特 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.74,0:36:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.25,0:36:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡危險 請快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.76,0:36:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼呢 您才應該趕快…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.89,0:36:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還沒回去 我們怎麼能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.15,0:36:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這武器真適合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.02,0:36:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.99,0:36:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.10,0:36:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.14,0:36:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫人救你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.62,0:36:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就不必了 倒是小子你…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.17,0:36:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找個地方藏起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.43,0:36:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裡現在到處是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.07,0:36:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.64,0:37:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 怎麼這麼難搞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.14,0:37:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.35,0:37:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾我只能送到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.52,0:37:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.52,0:37:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.19,0:37:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來打倒這個傢伙 請您無論如何要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.31,0:37:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.82,0:37:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.04,0:37:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.49,0:37:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.11,0:37:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜爾維
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.64,0:37:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.49,0:37:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.31,0:38:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這廝讓我來動手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.05,0:38:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.74,0:38:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈爾哥
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.75,0:38:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再磨磨蹭蹭的了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.06,0:38:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二城牆已經被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.28,0:38:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.13,0:38:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.27,0:38:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前跟那廝有筆賬要算
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.66,0:38:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經算清了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.33,0:38:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.11,0:38:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.63,0:38:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.97,0:38:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.75,0:38:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊大人 您沒事就…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.13,0:38:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把我放在這
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.19,0:38:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.20,0:38:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝爾鋒需要我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.43,0:38:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉第一外門
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.17,0:39:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒放手麼 真執著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.46,0:39:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.46,0:40:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.52,0:40:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如波爾庫斯將軍這樣見多識廣 都對那武器出乎意料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.33,0:40:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這是要幹什麼啊 霍茲爾陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.14,0:40:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.23,0:40:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呢 還不快去拿傘
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.78,0:40:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.54,0:40:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.83,0:40:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特 無能者在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.99,0:40:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了國家在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.74,0:40:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同敵軍大將戰鬥 操縱著未知的格雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.06,0:40:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令他的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.80,0:40:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是命令他 是請求他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.07,0:41:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想拒絕就可以拒絕 可萊卡特他拿起了劍
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.09,0:41:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那雙沒有魔力的手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.89,0:41:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區淋雨這點小事 何足掛齒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.92,0:41:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.21,0:41:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到這武器的極限在哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.63,0:41:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韌帶居然錘煉得如此結實
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.91,0:42:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.64,0:42:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.89,0:42:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.63,0:42:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.45,0:42:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快現身 你到底是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.17,0:42:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我看看你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.79,0:43:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.97,0:43:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑銀
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.17,0:43:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾妲 絃樂大賽伊奧肯定會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.01,0:44:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一日 正午稍前
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.34,0:44:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯將軍戰死的消息傳到大隊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.87,0:44:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波爾庫斯軍暫時撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.71,0:45:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條消息也立即傳到了本國的羅奇斯書記長處
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.72,0:45:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊歐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.59,0:45:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.62,0:45:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消息說在毗儺天攻略戰中曾目擊到她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.05,0:45:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在情況怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.29,0:45:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.22,0:45:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.54,0:45:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼也不能置之不理對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.03,0:45:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.80,0:45:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不要緊了 我去和家兄商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.67,0:45:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟我來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.27,0:45:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.80,0:45:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.12,0:45:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.88,0:45:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜爾維我說你冷靜下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.29,0:45:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 托爾將軍他…這是為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.19,0:45:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的事 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.98,0:45:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.59,0:45:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜爾維
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.56,0:46:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛金
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.75,0:46:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人悲傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.99,0:46:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.87,0:46:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事 我能走
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.22,0:46:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.17,0:46:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.67,0:46:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.19,0:46:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照約定
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.71,0:46:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.17,0:46:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊卡特
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.80,0:46:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑斯那傢伙還會再來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.85,0:47:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…還要繼續戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.87,0:47:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.79,0:47:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在這上面的就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.22,0:47:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷加茨 你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.91,0:47:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼沒事啊
